06:42.460 --> 06:44.820
so much adventure and excitement that humor would seem out of place.

06:44.820 --> 06:48.420
But noted science fiction and fantasy author El Sprague to Camp,

06:48.660 --> 06:51.380
thinks that humor and science fiction can mix very well.

